We benchmarked performance of REdiscoverTE against RepEnrich on RSEM simulated RNA-seq data. We followed default workflow of RepEnrich. Performance of REdiscoverTE and RepEnrich were evaluated using the metric MARD at the level of subfamily, where MARD is defined as in Salmon publication:15\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
