We then computed a TE demethylation enrichment score (Supplementary Table 3) as the ratio of within-TE methylation state (using DMC CpG sites in intergenic TEs) to global methylation state (using all DMC sites). This enrichment score is 1 when the methylation state in TE is comparable to that of the global methylation state, > 1 when a higher proportion of TE DMCs are demethylated, <1 when a smaller proportion of TE DMCs are demethylated.\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
